        "TileImage": "$($repository f5a89a5e-afc3-437d-8635-a4a8f272ce52).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47\rIntelligence has uncovered a discreet gathering of influential financiers in Sapienza. Behind their polished appearances lies a coordinated effort to manipulate global markets through illicit gold reserves.\rThese individuals operate with the same arrogance as a certain infamous magnate. Their meeting today presents us with a rare opportunity to dismantle their operation in one decisive strike.\rEliminate the targets, 47. Ensure their golden empire collapses with them.\rGood Luck",
